OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMichael Rosen wins         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchildren's poetry award    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fafter battling Covid-19    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Michael Rosen has won the Centre for   
OL,6, Literacy in Primary Education Poetry   
OL,7, Award (CLiPPA) for his collection of   
OL,8, poems about migration.                 
OL,10,FOn The Move saw Rosen reflect on his   
OL,11,Fown past as part of a Polish-Jewish    
OL,12,Ffamily growing up in London.           
OL,14,FThe collection was published in 2020   
OL,15,Fand was illustrated by Quentin Blake.  
OL,17,FThe chair of the judges, Allie Esiri,  
OL,18,Fdescribed the collection as "a timely -
OL,19,Fand timeless - reminder of our kinship 
OL,20,Fwith our fellow humans".               
